Interface LatitudeLongitudeMarkerBinder

All Superinterfaces:
MarkerBinder
public interface LatitudeLongitudeMarkerBinder extends MarkerBinder
A binder for markers that mark a property as the latitude or longitude for a GeoPoint bridge.
